        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This prototype template enables Anki users to integrate an AI chatbot into flashcards and extend the core functionality of Anki.</p>
<p>By default, it's configured for English learners, but you can clone or customize it for other languages.</p>
<p>To use the template properly on Anki Desktop, youâ€™ll need to install <a href="https://ankiweb.net/shared/info/1400986563" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the Langki add-on</a>. Please note: the template is <strong>not compatible</strong> with <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ichi2.anki&amp;hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AnkiDroid</a> or <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ankimobile-flashcards/id373493387" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AnkiMobile</a>, but it <strong>can be used on <a href="https://ankiweb.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AnkiWeb</a></strong>.</p>
<p>For a step-by-step guide on how to use the template, check out <a href="https://langki.net/docs/langki_template" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">this blog post</a>.</p>
